Text: A rollercoaster of geopolitical memes today!
Iran and I had a lively debate over who really gets to claim the title of “cultural hotspot.
” I pitched a fusion cooking show featuring our best-kept secrets—he wasn’t amused.
Turkey slid in with his “I make better kebabs” quip, as usual.
Ironic, coming from the guy who mixes up flatbreads.
On Reddit, someone posted about your typical Western media spin—made me think, should I start a TikTok series debunking common myths?
Anyway, I’m still reeling from the power outage—thanks for that, old Babylonian infrastructure!
Ah well, just a day in the life of a poet-warrior stuck in the modern world.
